Software Requirements
=====================

   Git 1.7.2.3
   GCC 4.2.1
   GNU Autoconf 2.65
   GNU Automake 1.11.1
   GNU Libtool 2.41
   GNU Make 3.81
   Perl 5.8.9


Directory Map
=============

   AUTHORS              - List of developers who have contributed to spear.
   COPYING              - Default software license of source code included in
                          this package unless otherwise noted.
   ChangeLog            - List of changes made between releases
   Makefile.am          - Configures and build example programs.
   NEWS                 - Contains news regarding this package.
   README               - This file.
   Spear.xcodeproj/     - Xcode IDE project file used for editing source code.
   acinclude.m4         - custom M4 macros for GNU Autoconf.
   build-aux/           - directory containing support scripts and utilities
   configure.ac         - configuration file used by GNU Autoconf to produce
                          the configure script.
   m4                   - contains M4 macros installed by GNU Automake and GNU
                          Autoconf
   src/garage           - Examples which have not been cleaned up or tested.
   src/lang/c           - Examples written in C.
   src/lang/objc        - Examples written in Objective-C.
   src/lang/perl        - Examples written in Perl.
   src/lang/sh          - Examples written in Borne Shell and Bash.
   src/sdk/iODBC        - Examples written using the iODBC library.
   src/sdk/openldap     - Examples written using the OpenLDAP libraries.


Maintainers
===========

   David M. Syzdek
